{"tid":2038699,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"初犯並判監不超過3個月，案底可被刪除","createTime":"2020-05-27T16:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T06:14:58.000Z","uid":163529,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"23077c8e3352aaa2b9b2677b795c49f05b1b0626","tid":2038699,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:51:32.000Z","msg":"在甚麼情況下，刑事案底可被刪除？<br />\n<br />\n當一個人被定罪後，留於警方或法庭之案底便不能被刪除（除非該罪犯上訴成功）。但根據《罪犯自新條例》（香港法例第297章）第2條，如罪犯是初犯者（即沒有其他案底），及<span style=\"color: red;\">被判處不超過3個月的監禁或罰款不超過10,000元，只要該罪犯在三年內不再犯案，其案底便可被視為「已喪失時效」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n如案底已喪失時效，該罪犯等同沒有被定罪一樣，因此，如他在求職時被僱主或其他人詢問有無犯過刑事罪，他可立即回答：「無」。該人不得因為沒有披露其案底而被解僱。<br />\n<br />\n但案底喪失時效之安排亦有例外情況。舉例，此安排不適用於高級公務員職位之求職者；如欲申請擔任或認可為律師、會計師、保險代理人或銀行董事，上述安排亦不適用（詳情可參閱《罪犯自新條例》第3條及第4條）。此外，如有關罪犯準備移民而向警方申請無犯罪紀錄証明書（俗稱「良民証」），警方仍會在這文件上列出有關案底，但會註明此案底在香港法律下已喪失時效。"},{"pid":"832baf61107630f82c0f5327e92b7adee22138d7","tid":2038699,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:51:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/policeAndCrime/criminal_liability_and_penalties/q4.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FpoliceAndCrime%2Fcriminal_liability_and_penalties%2Fq4.shtml&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32f4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=eb7b26b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/policeAndCrime/criminal_liability_and_penalties/q4.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"8607a6a72e8afe467a87cb5055cd6822dbee72eb","tid":2038699,"uid":111996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:30:05.000Z","msg":"不超過3個月 難"},{"pid":"8a9a4542307948d81004e7f31adb1068760771f4","tid":2038699,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:32:31.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n無論有冇用都好，都要俾手足知。"},{"pid":"f4a49e24558a292ffa667cafb3d2990c7890a8fe","tid":2038699,"uid":247192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:35:22.000Z","msg":"有用 推"},{"pid":"01c2d3547b1bcc6ac0ef49ecbf20335c703035f1","tid":2038699,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T18:31:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd8c92ebeda5671a4b77642cc360ee095756687b","tid":2038699,"uid":27250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T18:33:46.000Z","msg":"一樣有案底"},{"pid":"5ff7507894ed594bca9e3813fa5c9ad84a07e233","tid":2038699,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T18:35:43.000Z","msg":"美國唔會理，有良心雇主唔會理，其他國家都會跟美國唔會理。<br />\n<br />\n結果？港共自己打飛機啦。"},{"pid":"6de325e7d3a5ed976f2a82b5ebb3600fc0d4cf01","tid":2038699,"uid":324712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T20:21:41.000Z","msg":"有用、push"},{"pid":"bad1aae98e84b8bbeccdf1145394515e3e408647","tid":2038699,"uid":276693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T01:07:11.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"dce9c7ad208e497052173a8ff35842bbc4265922","tid":2038699,"uid":345377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d068e7ac9f148bd656b6f35b8df7de8c3922f04","tid":2038699,"uid":215325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:14:58.000Z","msg":"要如實講，問有無記錄同有無犯罪係兩件事。<br />\n我之前有去攞過意見，答案係要"}]}